text: Maciej Okręglak (born 5 July 1993 in Nowy Sącz) is a Polish slalom canoeist who has competed at the international level since 2009. He won a bronze medal in K1 team event at the 2017 European Championships in Tacen. He finished in 18th place in the K1 event at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro. ==References== == External links == * Maciej OKREGLAK at CanoeSlalom.net Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male canoeists Category:Olympic canoeists of Poland Category:Canoeists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Nowy Sącz
